<h2>Bibliothèque</h2><div id="node-3885" class="" >
<div class="vdc-post">
    <div class="vdc-post-body">
<div class="vdc-post-inner vdc-article">
<h2 class="vdc-postheader"><a href="/en/bibliobus" title="Bibliobus">Bibliobus</a></h2>
<div class="vdc-postcontent">
<div class="vdc-article"><p><span style="color: #e08832; font-size: 15.6000003814697px; font-weight: bold;">The Bibliobus returns in parks!</span></p>
<p><strong>From June 25 to September 3, 2015</strong></p>
<p>All summer long, between a soccer or a baseball game, take full advantage of books. Watch for the passing of the travelling book van in a park near you. There your chi.ldren will be able to borrow novels, cartoons, albums, documentaries and much more! Everything to satisfy their thirst for reading!</p>
<h3>From 4 to 6 p.m.</h3>
<p><strong>Monday</strong><br />Yvan-Franco park (de Gaulle et Desmarais)</p>
<div class="read_more"><a href="/en/bibliobus" title="Read the rest of Bibliobus.">Read more</a></div></div>

</div>
<div class="cleared"></div>
<div class="vdc-postfootericons vdc-metadata-icons">
         <a href="/bibliobus" title="Bibliobus " class="translation-link node_translation_fr">Français</a>&nbsp|&nbsp         <a href="http://twitter.com/?status=Bibliobus%20http%3A/%2Fwww.ville.chateauguay.qc.ca/en/bibliobus" class="tweet tweet_Twitter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;   Tags: <a href="/en/taxonomy/term/95" class="active">Bibliothèque</a>, <a href="/en/taxonomy/term/153">Library</a>
</div>

