<h2 class="vdc-postheader"><a href="/en/online-catalogue" title="Online Catalogue ">Online Catalogue </a></h2>
<div class="vdc-postcontent">
<div class="vdc-article"><p>To consult the online catalogue of the Châteauguay Municipal Library, please <a href="http://chateauguay.crsbp.qc.ca/uhtbin/cgisirsi/x/0/0/57/49?user_id=WEBSERVERE" target="_blank" title="Online catalogue of the Chateauguay Municipal Library">follow this link</a>.</p>
<p>For the&nbsp;user guide&nbsp;of the online catalogue, please <a href="http://www.ville.chateauguay.qc.ca/sites/default/files/Depliant-utilisation-catalogue-bibliotheque-English.pdf">click here</a>.</p>
